  <text>
      <body>
        
     
      <div xml:id="Clay"> 
              <interpGrp type="poembox">
                <interp ana="#form" type="FreeVerse"></interp>
                <interp ana="#tone" type="sad"></interp>
                <interp ana="#topic" type="love"></interp>
              </interpGrp>
             <lg> 
              <l>I dreamt that I dwelt in marble halls</l>
          <l>With vassals and serfs at my side</l> 
          <l>And of all who assembled within those walls</l>
          <l>That I was the hope and the pride.</l>
          <l>I had riches too great to count, could boast</l>
          <l>Of a high ancestral name,</l>
          <l>But I also dreamt, which pleased me most,</l>
          <l>That you loved me still the same.</l>
          
                 
